# Legacy hero videos (~381 MB tracked) — production uses hero-dark.* / hero-light.* only.
# Run once if already in git: git rm --cached public/video/177*.mp4 public/video/hero.mp4
public/video/177*.mp4
public/video/hero.mp4

# Admin uploads (~67 MB). Safe for GitHub (no file >100 MB). Uncomment to keep repo smaller;
